ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T01:20:06.000Z","msg":"「開放世界」呢個賣點由優點慢慢變左做伏點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"得rockstar同nintendo知咩係open world<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"得GTA既world係真係遊戲既一部分，其他既純粹要你由一個點行好撚耐去另一個點，中間個world其實毫無意義，你唔會有興趣去探索個world，每次去另一個點，都會覺得好煩厭"},{"pid":"d2c2de78e44ccdc3a5497afbd268b35646b3689d","tid":1125682,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d04dd0cfcc65a3818ac32beb35d1c3b2dcd851b8","tid":1125682,"uid":182786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"其實game一早做好，Sony仲唸住有隻WWZ 做對比，點知自己隻day gone 都係五十步笑百步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"如果一定要2揀一，我揀wwz啦"},{"pid":"5eda253a662adcd190a9d25075d3a9697eb69b37","tid":1125682,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a347531ba2434eb5a21981be90abc4ff12fd7a72","tid":1125682,"uid":74970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3ddf24e395b3af0565c4fd3803580d12ec432eba","tid":1125682,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a2a32d0c4bea11f84c5969144e8977ce6d6cfefd","tid":1125682,"uid":74970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"6.5係講緊anthem，fallout76之流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得7分差唔多，未算咁差既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"根本兩隻都唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:05:47.000Z","msg":"真心咩, 2隻個設計都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟本傻既先會諗到用fallout整online, 仲要cut晒npc, 整一隻刷驚<br />\n仲要用個唔岩整online驚既濕9 engine整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"呢兩隻都差<br />\nanthem一開波瘋狂斷線又多BUG<br />\n加上隻GAME好快就爆機刷刷刷<br />\n已經帶動唔到班玩家玩落去<br />\nfallout76唔洗講啦<br />\n班玩家對佢一D希望都無<br />\n最多只係fallout4 multiplayer DLC<br />\n隻驚都懶得再執<br />\nDAYS GONE 當初上E3都有幾多期望<br />\n獨佔加喪屍暴走<br />\n不過後期又delay<br />\n到出黎成品同玩家期望落差幾大<br />\n我剩係睇達哥玩左晚都覺得麻麻地<br />\n可以玩不過等二手囉<br />\n畫面唔突出故事太平淡無聊<br />\n一大堆系統塞落去就完事<br />\n我都係玩返隻狼先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce72cb71702b35df4a5c8534bcca3e2eb03be9f","tid":1125682,"uid":74927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:30:07.000Z","msg":"試玩左一陣 感覺只係一味接下任 <br />\n跟住走下CG 個D game 故事性麻麻<br />\n開電單車個控制我可以同你講係ON9<br />\n基本一開就撞 你老母轉彎難轉到呢<br />\n直程你轉彎好似俾野卡住左係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又多樹又多地圖物 <br />\n人物控制同the last of Us 差唔多一樣<br />\n但係論遊戲性同故事 一定冇the last of Us咁強<br />\n呢隻玩幾日會Feel 厭 除非後續更新加多D 玩法<br />\n係叫成堆喪屍衝出黎叫有新鮮感 <br />\n但係玩耐左就冇感覺 5分啦 10分滿分<br />\n真係好一般 係喪屍模式拉高番 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：機齡28年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45efb73dd2176b62e275efc4f7ef71ae5f0b5d1e","tid":1125682,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59b7f5772257b5820d3a0bf3d3466fd0d5f440c8","tid":1125682,"uid":49499,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"98e2847b8359392f0e8f1c0cc680f5ac98410eab","tid":1125682,"uid":78039,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"233ddf66d4209f0b610ceffea17c6b175cb10bf0","tid":1125682,"uid":75050,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T01:20:06.000Z","msg":"「開放世界」呢個賣點由優點慢慢變左做伏點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"得rockstar同nintendo知咩係open world<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"仲有cd projekt red"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"又真，唔記